  "body": "### Description\nAs a user I would like DNS entries to permit p2p connections when using the Besu permissioning contracts.\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n* DNS entries can be added to permit p2p connections\n* Sufficient testing has been added to ensure this feature works \n\n### Additional Information\nCurrently Besu code only handles IP addresses as entries in the permissioning contracts to check that a connection on the p2p network are permitted or not. \nSee NodeSmartContractPermissioningController\n",
